-----------------------------------------------------------
git
=================
1) login git
2) create repo
Note: repo name and local project name must be same
3) check remote connection
	git remote -v
4) git init
5) git remote add origin <pathof repo>
6) git add --all
7) git commit -m "message"
8) git push origin "name of branch"
9) git clone <git path>
10) npm install    (install node_modules folder) 

